WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:29.720
Welcome, so this week we have a grid set up.

00:29.720 --> 00:35.360
So pause the video and write down these diagrams if you need them for different ways to come

00:35.360 --> 00:37.000
into a grid.

00:37.000 --> 00:43.840
There's the simplest to a more advanced version, whatever your level.

00:43.840 --> 00:47.960
So we've already gone through the basics of getting to an obstacle or fence.

00:47.960 --> 00:51.920
It needs to be perpendicular and the horse needs to be traveling over the center of the

00:51.920 --> 00:53.320
obstacle.

00:53.320 --> 00:58.560
If your horse still has trouble with this, use only cross rails or start with the exercise

00:58.560 --> 01:01.640
at the poles on the ground.

01:01.640 --> 01:04.800
So first order of business is balance.

01:04.800 --> 01:10.400
You want your balance to be right over your toes and your feet, legs traveling up over

01:10.400 --> 01:14.920
your knees, through your hips and out over the top of your head.

01:14.920 --> 01:20.600
At every point through the grid, you want that balance to remain the same in your body.

01:20.600 --> 01:26.560
In order to do that, we need to bend our joints accordingly through the exercise and through

01:26.560 --> 01:30.560
the movement of the horse to absorb.

01:30.560 --> 01:39.200
Secondly, to keep our balance, the first thing we want to practice is grabbing main.

01:39.200 --> 01:45.440
The grid is a great place to learn to grab the main because the horse is only traveling

01:45.440 --> 01:46.480
in a straight line.

01:46.480 --> 01:48.760
There's no turns.

01:48.760 --> 01:55.320
So grab the main as you approach and keep a hold of it the whole time to keep your balance

01:55.480 --> 02:01.080
right over the center of gravity, which should be underneath your stirrup.

02:01.080 --> 02:05.560
The goal of today is to get your balance and be able to maintain it.

02:05.560 --> 02:12.880
First grabbing main and then being able to let go and not have to use your reins to use

02:12.880 --> 02:17.720
the main for balance using your core strength only.

02:17.720 --> 02:23.400
Trust your animal, trust the balance that you have and eventually you'll be able to

02:23.400 --> 02:24.040
let go.

